e","marker":3,"text":"Other mss add of heaven"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 66:6","book":"Isa","chapter":66,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the throne, saying, “It is done!” "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 66:6","book":"Isa","chapter":66,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add angel"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or bowl on the air"},{"marker":3,"text":"Other mss add of heaven"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:16:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There were flashes of lightning, rumblings, and peals of thunder. And a severe earthquake occurred like no other since people have been on the earth, so great was the quake. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 19:16–19","book":"Exo","chapter":19,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 4:5","book":"Rev","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 8:5","book":"Rev","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 11:19","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 19:16–19","book":"Exo","chapter":19,"verse":16},{"label":"Rv 4:5","book":"Rev","chapter":4,"verse":5},{"label":"Rv 8:5","book":"Rev","chapter":8,"verse":5},{"label":"Rv 11:19","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:16:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The great city "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 18:10","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 18:16","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 18:18","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 18:21","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":21,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" split into three parts, and the cities of the nations "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Or the Gentile cities"},{"kind":"text","text":" fell. Babylon the Great was remembered in God’s presence; he gave her the cup fi